quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  26,123,Aadinkoo…ďe …ďen fenniino Nulaa…ďe …ďen
  26,124,"Tuma nde Huudu musi…ó…óo ma…ď…ďe on wi'annoo …ďe: \"Enee, on hulataa [Alla]"
  26,125,"Min dey, ko mi Nulaa…óo e moo…óon hoolaa…óo"
  26,126,Hulee Alla …óofto…óon mi
  26,127,"Mi toraaki on e dow …óum njo…ďdi, njo…ďdi am ndin fawaaki si wanaa Jooma winndere nden"
  26,128,"Enee, on mahay maande e kala tulde hi…óon fija"
  26,129,"Jogito…óon ku…ďeeje a wi'ayma onon ko on luttintee…ďe [ka aduna]"
  26,130,"Si on jaggitii, janggiton ko ndunndarankoo…ďe"
  26,131,Hulee Alla …óofto…óon mi
  26,132,Hulee On …ďeydir…óo on ko anndu…óon
  26,133,O …ďeydiri on neemoraa…ói e …ďi…ó…ďe wor…ďe
  26,134,E gese e can…ói
  26,135,"[O maaki] min dey, mi…óo hulani on Lepte √Ďalaande mawnde"
  26,136,"∆Āe wi'i: \"No fotana men ter, si a waajike maa…óum si a laataaki jeyaa…óo e waajotoo…ďe …ďen"
  26,137,"Pellet, …óum wonaali si wanaa jikku adinoo…ďe …ďen"
  26,138,Menen men wonaali leptoytee…ďe
  26,139,"∆Āe fenni mo, Men halki …ďe. Pellet, wonii e …óum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] Aaya, …ďur…ďe heewude e ma…ď…ďe laataaki gom…óin…ďe"
  26,140,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko Kanko woni Teddu…óo Yurmetee…óo"